org.onyxplatform.api.java

Class OnyxMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.onyxplatform.api.java.OnyxMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OnyxNames
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EnvConfiguration, FlowCondition, Lifecycle, PeerConfiguration, Task, Trigger, Window

    public class OnyxMap
extends java.lang.Object
implements OnyxNames
    Serves as a base for any Onyx concept that is represented only by a map. Implementors include things like Tasks, LifecycleCall, FlowConditionEntry, WindowEntry, etc.
